itunes:title: Jamie Dana; Talking Instagram With The Social Media Queen Herself!
title: Jamie Dana; Talking Instagram With The Social Media Queen Herself!
description:
In this episode, Jessi and Stew chat with Social Media Guru, Jamie Dana! She is a hairstylist turned business owner and helps other stylist's build a business and life they love using Instagram. She gives great advice and talks about her experience and life transition as her following grew. 

FOLLOW JAMIE!

Instagram- @jamiedanahairstylist
Youtube- Jamie Dana
